Field Type Default Notes <code>autoConvert</code> boolean <code>true</code> Convert JSON results to TOON <code>delimiter</code> <code>comma\|tab\|pipe</code> <code>comma</code> Tabular delimiter <code>indent</code> int 0–8 <code>2</code> Spaces per level <code>flattenDepth</code> int ≥0 <code>4</code> &gt;0 enables safe key-folding <code>threshold</code> int ≥0 <code>100</code> Min chars before converting <pre><code>{
  "toon": {
    "autoConvert": true,
    "delimiter": "comma",
    "indent": 2,
    "flattenDepth": 4,
    "threshold": 100
  }
}
</code></pre>

Field Type Default Notes <code>enabled</code> boolean <code>true</code> <code>host</code> string <code>0.0.0.0</code> <code>port</code> int <code>3100</code> <code>publicUrl</code> string — Public-facing URL for OAuth redirects <code>auth.username</code> / <code>auth.passwordHash</code> string — Basic Auth credentials <p>Basic Auth is enabled when <code>MORPH_WEB_USERNAME</code> (env) is set; requests to <code>/api/*</code> and <code>/ws</code> are then challenged.</p> <pre><code>{
  "webUi": {
    "enabled": true,
    "host": "0.0.0.0",
    "port": 3101,
    "publicUrl": "https://morph.example.com"
  }
}
</code></pre>

Field Type Default Notes <code>intervalMs</code> int <code>30000</code> <code>timeoutMs</code> int <code>5000</code> <code>maxRetries</code> int <code>3</code> <pre><code>{
  "health": {
    "intervalMs": 30000,
    "timeoutMs": 5000,
    "maxRetries": 3
  }
}
</code></pre>
